Class MonoStereoMode

  • java.lang.Object

      • com.xxmicloxx.NoteBlockAPI.model.playmode.MonoStereoMode

  • public class MonoStereoMode
extends ChannelMode
    Ignores panning of Note and Layer from nbs format and plays mono Note as fake stereo at fixed offset from Player head.
